values: 三月；马奇（人名）；（march）行进；行军；长途跋涉；示威；游行；进展；进步；步伐；进行曲；（一段时间进行的）路程
（march）行进；行军；（军队）进人；齐步前进；使行进；前进；使前进；进发；出来；通过；游行示威；使…去；强迫…去
（M.Arch.）建筑学硕士（Master of Architecture的缩写）

synonym.mean: 行军，进军；进行曲；示威游行

word_group.brief_definition: 像三月里的野兔一样疯狂
像三月里的野兔一样疯狂
word_group.phrase: as mad as a March hare

bilingual.source: The parade will march down the main street tomorrow.
bilingual.target: 游行队伍明天将沿着主要街道前进。

bilingual.source: The march of science; the march of time.
bilingual.target: 科学的前进；时间的前进。

bilingual.source: March in single file or a narrow column
bilingual.target: 指部队单行或纵队前进

bilingual.source: The march of the human mind is slow.
bilingual.target: 人类思想前进的步伐是缓慢的。

bilingual.source: Thee officer ordered his soldiers to march.
bilingual.target: 长官命令他的士兵前进。

bilingual.source: Strike up the drum and march courageously.
bilingual.target: 让战鼓敲打起来,勇敢地前进吧!

bilingual.source: This is believed to be why they march in crowds.
bilingual.target: 这被认为是蝗虫以密集群体前进的原因.

list.abstract: MARCH大学（日文：マーチ）是指日本东京都的一个大学群的统称。由5所著名私立大学名称的罗马字首字母组成，是日本非常难考取的5所著名私立大学。

yingyinNormal.en: For Genghis! For Genghis! For Genghis! March!
yingyinNormal.zh: 为成吉思汗而战！为成吉思汗而战！出发！

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, no. No, you need to March me inside and make me pay now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不，不，你该押我进去，让我现在就付钱[付出代价] 。

yingyinNormal.en: There's no need for decrees. Or sermons to rouse. We march before they do. Go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没必要下令，也没必要战前昭告，我们要先发制人，出发。

yingyinNormal.en: We have to do something! We can't let him march on the valley, take his revenge!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们得马上行动，不能让太狼回到和谷村来报仇，荼害百姓。

yingyinNormal.en: And every other Saturday, he had to march in a parade and wave flowers at tyrants.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每两周的周六他都得参加游行，为一位暴君欢呼。

yingyinNormal.en: My brother, yes, we need not march, but at least marshal our forces. We must prepare.
yingyinNormal.zh: 兄弟，确实，我们还不用进兵，但至少应该整顿军队，我们必须做好准备。

yingyinNormal.en: I know what I said. I know what you said. I know what my mother said on March 5, 1992.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我说了什么，我也知道你说了什么，我还知道我妈在1992年3月5日说了什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Right, so march in there, brush your teeth and go to bed. But I don't want to go to bed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，所以进屋去，刷刷牙，上床睡觉。但我不想睡觉。

yingyinNormal.en: But the future, our future starts tomorrow at dawn. When we march together into the Capitol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但未来我们的未来，将在明日黎明我们进入国会区之时峥嵘初现。

yingyinNormal.en: "Saturday, March 3rd. 0705, meeting called to order. 0706, president gets shampoo in eye. 0707, meeting adjourned."
yingyinNormal.zh: "周六，3月3号。7点5分，开会。7点6分，主席的眼睛里沾了洗发水。7点7分，散会。"。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd march into hell for you, if I thought there was a slightest chance of victory. But there isn't, this is suicide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我觉得有半点机会的胜利，我会为你进军地狱，但目前还没有，这是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Hear me, Kublai. You have only half the men and horses you had on the last march. Kaidu has gone north. Banished north.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你听我一句，忽必烈，比上次进攻，你现在仅剩半数的兵马，海都又回了北方。放弃南征吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I was born in March 1979, what does it make me? You're zodiac animal is the goat. Well, I eat a lot, so I like the goat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是在1979年3月出生，那我属什么？那你是属羊的。嗯，我吃过不少，所以，我喜欢羊。

yingyinNormal.en: As you lead your sons back into the jaws of Sidao's China, I will march north to Karakorum to defend the true Mongol capital.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您带着您的儿子们往贾似道的中原虎口走，我会向北进军回哈拉和林去保卫我们真正的蒙古都城。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you realize that teaching is the first thing I've failed at since my ill-fated attempt to complete a chin-up in March of 1989?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知不知道，教书是我自从1989年3月做引体向上失败以后搞砸的第一件事。

yingyinNormal.en: I urged him to march upon Erebor, to rally the seven armies of the dwarves, to destroy the dragon and take back the Lonely Mountain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我敦促他进军艾雷博，集合矮人的七支大军消灭恶龙，收复孤山。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom! Lily, you are not in charge of what you wear, of breakfast, or anything. Now, put that backpack on and march it out to the car!
yingyinNormal.zh: 老妈！莉莉，衣着，早餐，还有其他事，都不是你说了算，现在，背上背包，朝着我们的车进发。

yingyinNormal.en: We also have a deposition from a young woman, a staffer, who says Goodwin posed as a volunteer at an event in Cincinnati on March 8th.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还得到一份来自一名年轻女性的证词，是一名职员，她说古德温在3月8日辛辛那提的一场活动中假扮成志愿者。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you march back in there and you own it, you let those people know that you're better than them, and you will be a legend. Okay. Yeah. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果你昂首阔步回到派对上，不以为耻反以为荣，你让那些乌合之众明白你比他们强，你就会是传奇人物了。好。没错。好？

yingyinNormal.en: So here's what's gonna happen. Okay? You're gonna go to that party, and you're gonna march up to that network guy, and you're gonna tell him, "Manny out!"
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以接下来这样，好吗？你要去参加那派对，大步走向那电视台老总，然后大声说“奶爸不干了”。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>March</highlight>, for the first time, wind and solar power accounted for more than 10 percent of the power generated in the US.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今年3月，风能和太阳能首次占美国发电量的10%以上。

examination_example.sentence: The US $3-million Fundamental Physics Prize is indeed an interesting experiment, as Alexander Polyakov said when he accepted this year's award in <highlight>March</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 正如亚历山大·波利亚科夫今年三月份接受奖项时所言，300 万美元的基础物理学奖确实是一项有趣的实验。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>March</highlight> 2010 a judge ruled that genes were unpatentable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2010年3月，一名法官裁定，基因不再授予专利。

examination_example.sentence: It is not by chance that the Funeral <highlight>March</highlight> is not the last movement of the Eroica Symphony, but the second.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 葬礼进行曲不是英雄交响曲的最后一个乐章而是倒数第二个乐章，这不是偶然。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>March</highlight>, a report revealed that H&M was struggling with $4.3 billion worth of unsold stock.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今年3月，一份报告显示，H&M积压了价值43亿美元的库存。

examination_example.sentence: Goddard launched his first rocket from an aunt's farm in his native Massachusetts in <highlight>March</highlight> 1926.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1926年3月，Goddard在家乡马萨诸塞州的一个阿姨农场发射了他的第一枚火箭。

examination_example.sentence: In a radio broadcast to the United States in <highlight>March</highlight> 1937, he deplored that broadcasting had become a one-way means of communication.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1937年3月，在一次面向美国的无线电广播中，他悲叹广播已成为一种单向的交流方式。

examination_example.sentence: But the snail continues its <highlight>march</highlight> to new territory, says Serra.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是这种水螺将会继续扩张到新的领地，塞拉特说道。

examination_example.sentence: "People are cheering and holding their carts in the air," says Giovanni Giorgio, who helped organize the <highlight>march</highlight> with a grass-roots organization called Generazione.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Giovanni Giorgio 说：“人们欢呼雀跃，将手推车举向空中。”他与一个名为 Generazione 的基层组织一起组织了游行。

examination_example.sentence: Each <highlight>March</highlight>, this village swells up in numbers, because it is located in the middle of a race that takes place every year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每年三月，这个村庄会人头涌涌，因为其位于每年举行的比赛赛段的中间地点。

examination_example.sentence: Why do a lot of people come to the village of Takotna every <highlight>March</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么每年三月都有很多人来塔科特纳村?

examination_example.sentence: The season runs June through August, with additional performances in <highlight>March</highlight> and September.

examination_example.sentence: Captain Scott had reached the South Pole early in 1912 but had died with his four companions on the <highlight>march</highlight> back.

examination_example.sentence_trans: 3月1日前加入我们的夏季摄影比赛。

examination_example.sentence: World famous physicist (物理学家) Stephen Hawking died peacefully at his home in Cambridge on <highlight>March</highlight> 14th, 2018.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2018年3月14日，世界著名物理学家斯蒂芬·霍金在剑桥的家中安详去世。

examination_example.sentence: Fifteen wild Asian elephants that left their home in Xishuangbanna last year are continuing to <highlight>march</highlight> north.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 去年离开西双版纳的15头野生亚洲象正在继续向北行进。
